T.J. Storm https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/T.J._Storm 0 Juan Ricardo Ojed, known professionally as T.J. Storm, is an American actor, stuntman, dancer and martial artist. The name "Storm" supposedly originated from one of the Karate styles he trained in.
